Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:52.82,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\blur4}瞬间撰写出意料之外的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.51,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\blur4}瞄准目标1！2！3！
